Used for demo/lab only.
Updates are done on a best-effort basis. 

The template are using ENV variables for Azurerm provider;
https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/azurerm/latest/docs

e.g ARM_TENANT_ID & ARM_SUBSCRIPTION_ID

Change region etc can be done in variables.tf file.
Update variable "ssh_public_key" or remove this configuration from k8.tf and varaibles.tf


